name: Summer Daydream pt3
description:
Maybe I will take the blue pill because sometimes I just wanted to see an old lady carry her things, young men doing his stuff, and I just sit down enjoying how the waves were breaks. I'm tired.  

The third issue, out of four issues from the Summer Daydreams series. Been shot using Diana plastic camera with Fujifilm Neopan Acros 100 120mm and animated with Adobe Photoshop.
